{
    "name": "Smoke Creeper",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Smoke Creeper",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Air And Smoke",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Elementals of smoke, such as the smoke creeper, are often cruel in their attacks on breathing creatures, causing them to choke and cough from their noxious fumes. Some believe that they hold secret allegiances to Ymeri, who holds domain over fire and smoke.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Monster Core 2",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 144",
                                "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 144",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 276
                            },
                            "page": 144
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Additional Lore",
                        "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                    },
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "Ymeri",
                            "alt": "Ymeri",
                            "game-obj": "Deities",
                            "aonid": 697
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "text": "Smoke creepers shift and modify their appearance as they float through the Plane of Air, but they prefer to take on a vaguely insectile form with wings trailing choking fumes and glowing red eyes.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Monster Core 2",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
